starvationevasion.common

Class MapConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.common.MapConverter

  • public class MapConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    class is used to convert between the spring2015code.model and the starvationevasion.client.Aegislash.GUI for converting between lat lon to x, y and back.

      • pointToMapPoint

        public MapPoint pointToMapPoint(java.awt.geom.Point2D p)
        Convert a Point in graphics-space to a MapPoint assuming the parallel of no distortion is the equator. This converts from a Plate-Caree projection back to lat and lon
        Parameters:
        p - Point to convert
        Returns:
        A MapPoint, reversing the projection defined by this class
